nodes.text: During the Galactic Civil War, a sixteen year-old female served at Alliance Base 16 on the planet Gaulus with her mother. After the base was razed by Imperial forces, she was one of the only survivors and attempted to set the base's power generator to explode. She was interrupted by Commander Harles of Garrison Company 125a, who allowed her to finish the job. She escaped with Harles and her badly wounded mother.
